{"tid":1977191,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[好野永存 派街坊]Final Fantasy 6 FFVI PC  繁體 繁中 正體中文","createTime":"2020-04-17T18:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T16:43:27.000Z","uid":226829,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"99e56c7aa6e83282ece97d27790599a080717583","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"近排各位巴絲，應該除左動森，就係忙緊FF7 remake。不過FF系列最神既，始終係上一代既FF6，但名氣一直遠不及7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要冇remake(反而FF3,4、聖劍傳說2，都有NDS級數remake)，得個同超任原版幾乎一樣(但容量大幾百倍)既remaster，可惜！同公司既另一神作chrono trigger又係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位煲7remake之餘，勿忘最神既6，亦希望有生之年見到6 remake！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteam入面既FF6，唔知做乜全東亞東南亞，包括日本都鎖晒區。就算轉到區買，都冇中文。就算去支那網搵民間漢化，都只有殘體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能全球獨家既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Final Fantasy 6 PC正體中文版</span></span></strong></span>，不能只有我玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。解壓後，無須任何設定，撳FF6.exe 就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">save5係超級初始存檔，全game第一個save point，全員LV99，最強武器防具x99，齊飾物x99，可快速通關，用唔用請自行斟酌，不喜勿用勿屌！</span></span>"},{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},{"pid":"294250e5e0e9023e61dfa5d2c8bae3b620695fa5","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:25.000Z","msg":"TINA BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47ca65936aa2ea884caa29b90f480a9e75f6145","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"有靚女女主角<br />\n<br />\n同埋滅世大魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c395c026ae6b459d0d2a410c21788dbec660b16","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_201910/16/-7s28Q5-7j06K1cT1kSfa-80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nga.178.com%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201910%2F16%2F-7s28Q5-7j06K1cT1kSfa-80.jpg&h=d1587007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古代美人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288667baaa13098812be7e29b2e683234012836b","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47ca65936aa2ea884caa29b90f480a9e75f6145","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like