ps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technobuffalo.com%2Fsites%2Ftechnobuffalo.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2Fwp%2F2015%2F04%2Fdissidia-final-fantasy-7.jpg&h=828dc29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jyWyRpla7hQ/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjyWyRpla7hQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=e31048e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d5b063fcadbdb3f82b829aac23c03cbda4af61","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:37:41.000Z","msg":"對眼好消魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942db95f3c305014a9cb4b8bb1666159e87219b","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thefinalfantasy.com/gallery/wallpaper/ff6/ff6-wallpaper-celes-and-locke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thefinalfantasy.com%2Fgallery%2Fwallpaper%2Fff6%2Fff6-wallpaper-celes-and-locke.jpg&h=f1df5787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd1da9cf31577316713cff943f6c7f503871b01","tid":1977191,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T21:38:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩想補ff6 <br />\n<br />\n呢個咩版黎 點解有繁中"},{"pid":"823f78a86e9ab6dbdd02deb1adb1048d47fd08d4","tid":1977191,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"FF6 連埋隱藏角色唔記得總共有13定14個角色，<br />\n仲要係同時使用，最後迷宮甚至係要你係果十幾人裏面分開3隊同時進行，<br />\n互相幫其他小隊開路。<br />\n呢點唔好話FF系列裏面獨有，<br />\n甚至係JRPG史上都冇乜遊戲可以做到呢個規模(接近既我只記得「貝獸物語」系列」)。<br />\n<br />\n另外十幾人裏面係全部都有詳細既角色故事線，你係可以見到佢人物既設定係好仔細。唔同角色既特技都唔同，有要你好似格鬥GAME咁輸入格鬥指令既，有變身既，有機械系既，有撚狗系(狗同伴)。<br />\n<br />\n仲有當年既音效下，歌劇院果段真係勁到痴線，<br />\n我唔明點解D 音效聲會做到佢真係唱緊歌咁有晒音調，<br />\n我真係好想睇次世代畫面下既歌劇院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117e269e56e5567e0728d9f46deb8192d50d5000","tid":1977191,"uid":15939,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"FF6 係好玩姐，成日話好神，神條命咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係FFVII FFX面前爭一班啦"},{"pid":"a14db942d157a28a62261488f848d8cf45cf3b84","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"288667baaa13098812be7e29b2e683234012836b","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47ca65936aa2ea884caa29b90f480a9e75f6145","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"有靚女女主角<br />\n<br />\n同埋滅世大魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"得靚唔夠㗎<br />\n你講的FF7有晒<br />\nFF10更加Yuna<br />\n唔係世界觀好完整的話<br />\n好難令人玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"標題味講左係PC版囉"},{"pid":"170580c94b800010a275aa5024172a54322b836d","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"288667baaa13098812be7e29b2e683234012836b","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47ca65936aa2ea884caa29b90f480a9e75f6145","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"有靚女女主角<br />\n<br />\n同埋滅世大魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"得靚唔夠㗎<br />\n你講的FF7有晒<br />\nFF10更加Yuna<br />\n唔係世界觀好完整的話<br />\n好難令人玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"7,10既靚女唔係第一主角，6既靚女係，一開始控制係佢，但其實FF6幾乎所有入隊角色都係主角，亦係唯一一集FF做到咁既設定。<br />\n<br />\n6可入隊人數14人(其實有D唔算係「人」)，係FF系列最多，仲要係唯一一集可收FF吉祥物莫古利入隊。<br />\n<br />\n6係FF唯一一集滅世大魔王真係滅到世，連世界地圖都唔同晒。滅世後，收返4個隊員同飛空艇，就進入開放世界，繼續搵其他人又得，打支線又得，直接打final  boss又得，當年黎講走得好前。<br />\n<br />\n我第一次玩既FF就係6，講真，好後悔第一次就玩6，之後玩過3,4,4-2,5,7,7cc,8,9,10,12,13-1，每一隻都比唔到6既震撼感。就好似玩絕不可劇透既ADV，第一次就玩Ever17一樣。至今6仲會隔幾年就重玩一次。<br />\n<br />\nign 既 top 100 RPG，FF6排第2，第1係同公司同期既Chrono Trigger。<br />\n<br />\n其他出名RPG排名<br />\n7.聖劍傳說2<br />\n10.巫師3<br />\n13.Persona 4 Golden<br />\n18.FF Tactics<br />\n22.FF 4<br />\n27.Bloodborne<br />\n31.FF 12<br />\n33.DQ 5<br />\n40.FF 9<br />\n49.Xenoblade Chronicles<br />\n50.Persona 5<br />\n52.FF 7 (？，真心覺得冇理由咁後，更冇理由後過FF4,12)<br />\n65.DQ 8<br />\n83.FF 1"},{"pid":"d71a1d048e93fc4331239b127582223761c3b9a5","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"823f78a86e9ab6dbdd02deb1adb1048d47fd08d4","tid":1977191,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"FF6 連埋隱藏角色唔記得總共有13定14個角色，<br />\n仲要係同時使用，最後迷宮甚至係要你係果十幾人裏面分開3隊同時進行，<br />\n互相幫其他小隊開路。<br />\n呢點唔好話FF系列裏面獨有，<br />\n甚至係JRPG史上都冇乜遊戲可以做到呢個規模(接近既我只記得「貝獸物語」系列」)。<br />\n<br />\n另外十幾人裏面係全部都有詳細既角色故事線，你係可以見到佢人物既設定係好仔細。唔同角色既特技都唔同，有要你好似格鬥GAME咁輸入格鬥指令既，有變身既，有機械系既，有撚狗系(狗同伴)。<br />\n<br />\n仲有當年既音效下，歌劇院果段真係勁到痴線，<br />\n我唔明點解D 音效聲會做到佢真係唱緊歌咁有晒音調，<br />\n我真係好想睇次世代畫面下既歌劇院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:24:41.000Z","msg":"我第一次玩FF就係超任既6，配當時小說式既超任一族攻略，真係驚為天人。當時94年，晚晚半夜唔訓，一部電視機玩FF6、另一部電視機開著94世界盃，感覺正到一流。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見6咁正，之後搵5黎玩，感覺完全唔係嗰回事，可能係因為冇咁詳細既攻略。<br />\n<br />\n到7，冇PS，焗著遲成年有多，等98年PC版，好似話晝質已比PS版強化，但我就覺得，雖然係轉做3D，但點解好似差過6咁？超任版既6，背景細緻到嚇死人，7就爆晒格起晒狗牙？真係唔多開胃，加上當時冇乜時間玩，又冇超任一族寫得咁好既攻略，勉強玩完都唔知佢up乜。<br />\n<br />\n8都係差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n之後好多年，FF系列都冇出PC版(11係有，但 online我冇興趣)，我當時又唔想買PS、PS2，我就冇再理了。係近幾年再出返PC至玩返。<br />\n<br />\n十幾年後，XX痕想玩返7，先知套陳年老翻碟喺WIN7係run唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，上網搵到個2012年remaster版仲居然有繁中漢化(留意返 FF7喺remake之前，係從來冇任何官方中文版)，至第一次用合理畫質同明白劇情之下玩到7。"},{"pid":"d906b992d35b2a4109eea6aca75aa629600157bb","tid":1977191,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"3D初期畫面冇2D咁精緻都係正常"},{"pid":"f288319df47ee55410945693253231e3c8a33a36","tid":1977191,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"8546e7f57563802cb544e3efd1d2a0a97941f1bf","tid":1977191,"uid":98498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932ff91c09d77aa5d0c6df556e94c6c9ecfc5004","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8546e7f57563802cb544e3efd1d2a0a97941f1bf","tid":1977191,"uid":98498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029b8dae85e499020e098438430d4d27c895931f","tid":1977191,"uid":98498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩先開game, 樓主仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻game 係咪要用xbox手製先玩到? ps4手製+轉換程式 一按製就關左隻game"},{"pid":"13ed9c2f4bd9f201155b0ac3cdd6de49a3e469d6","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029b8dae85e499020e098438430d4d27c895931f","tid":1977191,"uid":98498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩先開game, 樓主仲係唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻game 係咪要用xbox手製先玩到? ps4手製+轉換程式 一按製就關左隻game"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:44:12.000Z","msg":"ps4手製+轉換程式 冇試過<br />\n我一向用xboxone手掣"},{"pid":"a45884b5f373e398b614247677b6fc1ad79015d4","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"932ff91c09d77aa5d0c6df556e94c6c9ecfc5004","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8546e7f57563802cb544e3efd1d2a0a97941f1bf","tid":1977191,"uid":98498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"sorry睇錯 FF6<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFF7有非官方繁中，我以前玩過，但玩完就DEL了<br />\n而家玩remark啦"},{"pid":"a09de409946f2b14e5a84ad4a68d47b55df13a42","tid":1977191,"uid":278837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e56c7aa6e83282ece97d27790599a080717583","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"近排各位巴絲，應該除左動森，就係忙緊FF7 remake。不過FF系列最神既，始終係上一代既FF6，但名氣一直遠不及7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要冇remake(反而FF3,4、聖劍傳說2，都有NDS級數remake)，得個同超任原版幾乎一樣(但容量大幾百倍)既remaster，可惜！同公司既另一神作chrono trigger又係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位煲7remake之餘，勿忘最神既6，亦希望有生之年見到6 remake！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteam入面既FF6，唔知做乜全東亞東南亞，包括日本都鎖晒區。就算轉到區買，都冇中文。就算去支那網搵民間漢化，都只有殘體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能全球獨家既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Final Fantasy 6 PC正體中文版</span></span></strong></span>，不能只有我玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。解壓後，無須任何設定，撳FF6.exe 就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">save5係超級初始存檔，全game第一個save point，全員LV99，最強武器防具x99，齊飾物x99，可快速通關，用唔用請自行斟酌，不喜勿用勿屌！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:22:19.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於可以玩番仲要中文版, 但我想問解完之後但冇聲...係唔係我整少乜野"},{"pid":"37ef1c787272fadb3995c206cd3d146694b3a813","tid":1977191,"uid":237415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"用ps4手掣一開就彈驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a895f717af1f6d41723fd2fcd4b359fceda758fc","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"有巴打話冇聲，有冇入game後入「設定」度睇過？<br />\n<br />\n我試過3部電腦，有2011年既古董文書機(幾年前用呢部機玩)有gameing PC有文書PC，有WIN7 有WIN10，全部都有聲，真係唔明點解巴打話冇聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於話用PS4手掣玩彈game，我試到係，WIN10認到PS4手掣，但入得game係冇反應。我玩PC game一向係用XBOX one手掣。同埋呢隻game可以用keyboard"},{"pid":"3722c1f581a9dc8aa3ae3649e4bd67d1b7788f82","tid":1977191,"uid":278837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a895f717af1f6d41723fd2fcd4b359fceda758fc","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"有巴打話冇聲，有冇入game後入「設定」度睇過？<br />\n<br />\n我試過3部電腦，有2011年既古董文書機(幾年前用呢部機玩)有gameing PC有文書PC，有WIN7 有WIN10，全部都有聲，真係唔明點解巴打話冇聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於話用PS4手掣玩彈game，我試到係，WIN10認到PS4手掣，但入得game係冇反應。我玩PC game一向係用XBOX one手掣。同埋呢隻game可以用keyboard"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"只能話我部all in one 唔知出咩事, 設定較到最大聲同都冇聲...聽youtube同netfix 又冇事..."},{"pid":"5520f296ba8a63c094e8b3656b1040f59950d33a","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170580c94b800010a275aa5024172a54322b836d","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"288667baaa13098812be7e29b2e683234012836b","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47ca65936aa2ea884caa29b90f480a9e75f6145","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"有靚女女主角<br />\n<br />\n同埋滅世大魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"得靚唔夠㗎<br />\n你講的FF7有晒<br />\nFF10更加Yuna<br />\n唔係世界觀好完整的話<br />\n好難令人玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"7,10既靚女唔係第一主角，6既靚女係，一開始控制係佢，但其實FF6幾乎所有入隊角色都係主角，亦係唯一一集FF做到咁既設定。<br />\n<br />\n6可入隊人數14人(其實有D唔算係「人」)，係FF系列最多，仲要係唯一一集可收FF吉祥物莫古利入隊。<br />\n<br />\n6係FF唯一一集滅世大魔王真係滅到世，連世界地圖都唔同晒。滅世後，收返4個隊員同飛空艇，就進入開放世界，繼續搵其他人又得，打支線又得，直接打final  boss又得，當年黎講走得好前。<br />\n<br />\n我第一次玩既FF就係6，講真，好後悔第一次就玩6，之後玩過3,4,4-2,5,7,7cc,8,9,10,12,13-1，每一隻都比唔到6既震撼感。就好似玩絕不可劇透既ADV，第一次就玩Ever17一樣。至今6仲會隔幾年就重玩一次。<br />\n<br />\nign 既 top 100 RPG，FF6排第2，第1係同公司同期既Chrono Trigger。<br />\n<br />\n其他出名RPG排名<br />\n7.聖劍傳說2<br />\n10.巫師3<br />\n13.Persona 4 Golden<br />\n18.FF Tactics<br />\n22.FF 4<br />\n27.Bloodborne<br />\n31.FF 12<br />\n33.DQ 5<br />\n40.FF 9<br />\n49.Xenoblade Chronicles<br />\n50.Persona 5<br />\n52.FF 7 (？，真心覺得冇理由咁後，更冇理由後過FF4,12)<br />\n65.DQ 8<br />\n83.FF 1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"仲有係第一部重機械元素既FF<br />\n<br />\nBTW雖然14人都係主角,但我好似記得雪人同GOGO係好少劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2822e24583bfaeab3b3b41bca56cc24eadd7a907","tid":1977191,"uid":165806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99e56c7aa6e83282ece97d27790599a080717583","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"近排各位巴絲，應該除左動森，就係忙緊FF7 remake。不過FF系列最神既，始終係上一代既FF6，但名氣一直遠不及7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要冇remake(反而FF3,4、聖劍傳說2，都有NDS級數remake)，得個同超任原版幾乎一樣(但容量大幾百倍)既remaster，可惜！同公司既另一神作chrono trigger又係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位煲7remake之餘，勿忘最神既6，亦希望有生之年見到6 remake！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteam入面既FF6，唔知做乜全東亞東南亞，包括日本都鎖晒區。就算轉到區買，都冇中文。就算去支那網搵民間漢化，都只有殘體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能全球獨家既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Final Fantasy 6 PC正體中文版</span></span></strong></span>