ormal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴南<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>交待到佢死<br />\n<br />\n天幻網，13年後冇update過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd78cfabe918003b050df4d25536523156dea937","tid":1977191,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"4先最神"},{"pid":"9a92c18aaf5863d7e3a140808a5820421aed70a9","tid":1977191,"uid":51014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b24bcfcbf107722a31c120b4db0ef455273e009","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e97da5d36eec9aa67541eb87ea1673d7c82b6c","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213ff9152c0ac03c75f1c3dc0930740ff69282f1","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"巴南有交待到佢死，係爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同帝國講和後，佢一直喺帝國首都行黎行去，好似帝國反口之後就再冇見到佢，應該都係兇多吉少.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前喺支那game網，見過有漢化組話破解晒全game對白資料庫，的確係再冇提佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:20:52.000Z","msg":"應該係天幻網<br />\n以前黎計，雖然係殘體，但以主攻FF既中文網黎講佢d資料肯定最齊<br />\n不過半收皮狀況好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"上面唔知做乜錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴南<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>交待到佢死<br />\n<br />\n天幻網，13年後冇update過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"當年d人都係估巴南死係帝國"},{"pid":"04c9e64e760be91e1c6094fcf0b5506608fd5956","tid":1977191,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"其實冇話邊個神啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過6代係故事同玩法方面都幾完整冇咩缺點挑剔<br />\n10幾個角色但基乎每個角色描寫都完整<br />\n有1-2隻好似比較路人（一隻好似係雪怪）"},{"pid":"d6c63541bd01124c6ffa345090744db1f467517d","tid":1977191,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823f78a86e9ab6dbdd02deb1adb1048d47fd08d4","tid":1977191,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a0ab3b951fd5906e3351f2ec758d88392c6a367d","tid":1977191,"uid":60315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde1ff8009ac14f4eb670aa41f18baed2621870","tid":1977191,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇玩過FF6<br />\n可以講下FF6點解最神<br />\n明明有FF7 同FF10係度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"FF6 連埋隱藏角色唔記得總共有13定14個角色，<br />\n仲要係同時使用，最後迷宮甚至係要你係果十幾人裏面分開3隊同時進行，<br />\n互相幫其他小隊開路。<br />\n呢點唔好話FF系列裏面獨有，<br />\n甚至係JRPG史上都冇乜遊戲可以做到呢個規模(接近既我只記得「貝獸物語」系列」)。<br />\n<br />\n另外十幾人裏面係全部都有詳細既角色故事線，你係可以見到佢人物既設定係好仔細。唔同角色既特技都唔同，有要你好似格鬥GAME咁輸入格鬥指令既，有變身既，有機械系既，有撚狗系(狗同伴)。<br />\n<br />\n仲有當年既音效下，歌劇院果段真係勁到痴線，<br />\n我唔明點解D 音效聲會做到佢真係唱緊歌咁有晒音調，<br />\n我真係好想睇次世代畫面下既歌劇院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"魔法女將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果首歌我仲記得<br />\n可以係2D pixel做到啲咁既效果好勁"},{"pid":"7a3f8092967402e6c10cddf531120fc76f4de1b5","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd78cfabe918003b050df4d25536523156dea937","tid":1977191,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20