faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提一提你FF2個升級系統痴痴地<br />\n佢用熟練度系統，例如升hp要俾人打 扣得多血先會升<br />\n所以後期d怪唔夠勁既話，要自己打自己先升到hp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d9b0e823a3100cac91094c9ec137b7bbf7fcf9","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39d3922c1fc8ac1872d63601848e8daee9aa2f5c","tid":1977191,"uid":189926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c395c026ae6b459d0d2a410c21788dbec660b16","tid":1977191,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_201910/16/-7s28Q5-7j06K1cT1kSfa-80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nga.178.com%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201910%2F16%2F-7s28Q5-7j06K1cT1kSfa-80.jpg&h=d1587007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古代美人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T12:28:53.000Z","msg":"如果重製應該同艾亞莉絲差唔多款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"J死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bf7292e32086e372c9f07f93db0f499fb0256c","tid":1977191,"uid":33999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e56c7aa6e83282ece97d27790599a080717583","tid":1977191,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"近排各位巴絲，應該除左動森，就係忙緊FF7 remake。不過FF系列最神既，始終係上一代既FF6，但名氣一直遠不及7<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要冇remake(反而FF3,4、聖劍傳說2，都有NDS級數remake)，得個同超任原版幾乎一樣(但容量大幾百倍)既remaster，可惜！同公司既另一神作chrono trigger又係！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位煲7remake之餘，勿忘最神既6，亦希望有生之年見到6 remake！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteam入面既FF6，唔知做乜全東亞東南亞，包括日本都鎖晒區。就算轉到區買，都冇中文。就算去支那網搵民間漢化，都只有殘體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能全球獨家既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Final Fantasy 6 PC正體中文版</span></span></strong></span>，不能只有我玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。解壓後，無須任何設定，撳FF6.exe 就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">save5係超級初始存檔，全game第一個save point，全員LV99，最強武器防具x99，齊飾物x99，可快速通關，用唔用請自行斟酌，不喜勿用勿屌！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"有無Level 1 全道具開局嘅save<br />\nlv99 好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf36668dbd6cc55baf220dfae8712c00375e678e","tid":1977191,"uid":139468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3f8092967402e6c10cddf531120fc76f4de1b5","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd78cfabe918003b050df4d25536523156dea937","tid":1977191,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"4先最神"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"FF4個世界觀都大<br />\nRydia 2個年齡性格轉變幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd455f73e740be0a84cab31fa0c987218133f3c","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf36668dbd6cc55baf220dfae8712c00375e678e","tid":1977191,"uid":139468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3f8092967402e6c10cddf531120fc76f4de1b5","tid":1977191,"uid":107490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd78cfabe918003b050df4d25536523156dea937","tid":1977191,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"4先最神"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"FF4個世界觀都大<br />\nRydia 2個年齡性格轉變幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"FF4我係psp先玩番，個感覺只係好膚淺咁覺得龍騎做兵好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋終於見識到鼎鼎大名既4天王，但原來只係普通boss戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe after year都無玩<br />\nFF6真係我第一隻拎上手玩既FF，當年個opera真係好震撼(不過個時已經出左FF7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}